result.name: Hoi Wan Vegetarian Restaurant

reviews.text:
Although their restaurant's name has the "vegetarian" word, their meat dishes are just as superb as their vegetable dishes. The chicken is seriously one of the best foods I ever had in Hong Kong and I just love how rustic and fresh the ingredients are. I guess its from the local produce.

With good value of money as well, I say its worth to stop by if you are going to Tai O which is near this restaurant.

No English menu, but three employees during our visit spoke great English made great recommendations! Very clear about dishes with meat, and without meat. Everything was very tasty.
Plus, they are open later than many restaurants in Tai O, we are currently eating at 8 pm on a Friday and they are hopping.
I really enjoyed the dishes here. It was some of the best white fish I’ve had.
Great food. Although it's a vegetarian restaurant, chicken is the best food it served. Don't miss this out.
You feel welcome

result.name: 海韻素食菜館

reviews.text: 👍👍👍地道風味！
吃過一次全數及一次團餐，團餐分量夠，但味道有點參差。妹妹去即場吃的八寶鴨讚不絕口。買了一隻回家吃，覺得未夠完備，基本蓮子栗子都唔夠腍。內餡全是栗子蓮子鹹蛋黃，我記得食過另外一家公司是有糯米的 ，但這隻沒有。白粥好受團友歡迎，但我覺得有點鹹。芋頭魚做得好但醬汁甜多鹹少。
